<el-popover
  ref="popover"
  placement="bottom-start"
  trigger="click"
  @show="onShowPopover"
  @hide="onHidePopover"
>
  <tree-conent
    :options="options"
    v-model="valueModel"
    @selected="change"
    @fn-init-label="initLabel"
  ></tree-conent>
  <el-input
    slot="reference"
    ref="input"
    v-model="labelmodel"
    clearable
    suffix-icon="el-icon-arrow-down"
    @change="valueModel=''"
    :placeholder="placeholder"
  ></el-input>
</el-popover>
